. בשעה שהמלך נמנה עם אילו נמצאי שלמים ובשעה שהמלך עוד נמנה עם אילו נמצאו שלמי'
         </quote>
                  <bibl default="false" status="draft">
                     <ref type="witness">94,9</ref>
                     <ref type="witness">III 1181:5</ref>
                  </bibl>
                  <cit type="translation">
<!-- The english translation of the passage is encoded in a nested cit element -->
                     <quote xml:lang="en">“R. Yiṣḥaq said:
It may be compared to the two royal legions, 
the Decumani and the Augustiani. When the emperor is counted with the former 
they are complete, and when he is counted with the latter they are complete.” (Freedman / Simon II 876)
<!-- The english translation of the passage-->
